{"lemma":"شِقاقِ","slug":"شِقاقِ","root":"ش.ق.ق","root_slug":"ش-ق-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ق-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شِقاق","root":"شقق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22705","n22710"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%90%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"suppurating or exudating blisters at the feet and/or carpus","examples":[{"text":"ويقولون في رِجْلِي شُقَاقٌ. والصَواب شُقُوقٌ. والصَواب شُقُوقٌ, فأمّا الشُّقَاقُ فَداء من أدواء الدّوابّ وهي صُدوعٌ في حوافرها وأرساغها.","english":"They say “in my feet is šuqāq.” The right form is šuqūq. šuqāq is a disease of beasts, blisters around the hoops or knees of them."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَاقَّ (šāqqa) (form III)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"discord, dissension","examples":[{"text":"ذٰلِكَ بِأَنَّ ٱللّٰهَ نَزَّلَ ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ بِٱلْحَقِّ وَإِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱخْتَلَفُوا فِي ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ لَفِي شِقَاقٍ بَعِيدٍ","english":"Those who are at variance with the book are indeed in a remote schism."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"draper","tags":["al-Andalus"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of شِقَّة (šiqqa)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃu.qaːq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22705","headword_ar":"شُقَاقٌ","root":"$q","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cracking in several places,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$aq~uqN","text_ar":"تَشَقُّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cracks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain disease occasioning cracks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the pasterns of horses"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and in their hoofs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and sometimes rising to their shanks:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says Yaakoob: (S:) and, accord. to Lth, (Mgh,) and Az, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cracking in several places"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$aq~uqN","text_ar":"تَشَقُّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the skin, from cold or some other cause, in the hands"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms, and the face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:) or it signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any crack,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slit, in the skin, from disease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) As says that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arm, and the foot"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leg, of a human being,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the fore leg and kind leg of an animal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:) but this is inconsistent with what is said by Yaakoob [as stated voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~N","text_ar":"شَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence]. (Mgh.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoEadu","text_ar":"اَسْعَدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arajN","text_ar":"شَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","M","S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n22710","headword_ar":"شَقَّاقٌ","root":"$q","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", meaning One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who glories,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"boasts, vainly, and praises himself for that which is not in him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not of the [classical] language of the Arabs. (L, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}